item.title: Whats wrong with this compiler?
item.dc:creator: @armeredman7 armeredman7
item.description:
@armeredman7 wrote:

First I’d download J2SE Development kit(or JDK for short) 5.0 update 9
Second I’d download J2SE Runtime Environment(or JRE for short) 5.0 update 9

Then make your compile look like:

@echo off
COLOR 08
title Project 16 Client
“C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.5.0_09\bin\javac” -cp . *.java
“C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.5.0_09\bin\java” server
pause
